CBRE are pleased to present 32 Clinker Street, Darra for Sale via Expressions of Interest.

Features of the site include:
- 90sqm Corporate grade ground floor offices
- 1,000sqm Clearspan warehouse area
- 4,000sqm General Industry land
- Warehouse access via multiple roller doors
- Over 2,500sqm of concrete hardstand
- Fully secured premium grade facility

Located in Darra's highly sought after QCL Estate approximately 15 minutes southwest of the Brisbane CBD and 15 kilometres north east of the Ipswich CBD. The property offers direct access to major arterials including the Ipswich, Logan and Centenary Motorways and the new Legacy Way Tunnel.

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact Mark Gilbride the Exclusive Agent.

- 335sqm Corporate office & showroom

- Fully secured and alarmed site

Located approximately 14 kilometres south west of the Brisbane CBD, within close proximity to both the Centenary Motorway and Western Freeway. The property is located on the corner of Sudbury and Northolt Street with access via single crossover providing a corporate aspect to the development.

The property includes:
- 120sqm Warehouse
- 180sqm First class office
- Ample parking
- 6 metre ceilings and Hi bay lighting
- Electric container-height roller door
- Tilt panel construction

For more information please contact CBRE exclusive agents.

One of the few sub 1,000sqm freestanding industrial investments available in the Western corridor. The site is located on Manburgh Terrace situated just 20 minutes (12 radial kilometres) from the Brisbane CBD and within minutes' drive from major arterial links such as the Ipswich and Centenary Motorways.

This freestanding facility features:
+ 524sqm Industrial Land
+ 20sqm of office & amenities
+ 270sqm of clearspan warehouse
+ 3-phase power
+ Access via Container height roller door
+ Flood free
+ Adjacent to the Darra Train Station

Tenant details:
+ Total income: $42,316.80 + Outgoings + GST
+ Lease expiry: 31st January 2021
+ Security: Personal Guarantee in place

For Sale via Public Auction On Site Thursday 22nd June 2017 at 11:00am

For further information please contact the Exclusive Agent David Savoff of CBRE.
